    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop the <strong>tomato<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> into wedges</p><p>Dissolve the <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 100ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[150ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
